A test case for the model object 'SAbstract Annotation'.

The following features are tested:

  • SNS
  • SName
  • SValue
  • SValue Type

The following operations are tested:

  • Get SValue STEXT
  • Get SValue SBOOLEAN
  • Get SValue SNUMERIC
  • Get SValue SFLOAT
  • Get SValue SURI
  • Get SValue SOBJECT
